{"tid":913610,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"唔吹奏陳奕迅，嚴選佢最差嘅Live","createTime":"2018-11-23T13:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T02:57:36.000Z","uid":69850,"like":12,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"89962fa062fddb17e14fed485661758685ee3fa4","tid":913610,"uid":69850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T13:49:45.000Z","msg":"2013年度叱咤<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RG6KpA3coUI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRG6KpA3coUI&d=XETi2Bt%2BZpnTLEalwkJRlhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=94203f7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RG6KpA3coUI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yEicE0ICikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyEicE0ICikw&d=XETi2Bt%2BZpnTLEalwkJRlhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=fc72adf1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yEicE0ICikw</a><br />\n2016年度叱咤<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gY6GtcN7cIM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgY6GtcN7cIM&d=XETi2Bt%2BZpnTLEalwkJRlhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=bfed2d24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gY6GtcN7cIM</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>跟住冇啦</strong>，根本佢唱得唔好嘅Live就係得呢兩年嘅叱咤，13年就情緒病，16年就根本冇諗過要唱四季嘅Live所以冇準備過（首歌原本唔係佢嘅，加上佢個晚準備來唱歌頌），唱得唔好就計計埋埋得個幾次，但有班人就永遠都用呢兩次嘅表現來唱衰Eason，踩到變地底泥為止，人哋過百次好正嘅Live提都唔提，永遠捉住啲柒事來鞭屍</span><br />\n<br />\n唔係想吹奏盲捧，只係攞返個公道<br />\n<br />\n同時送上Eason為四季自責影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V6GS6VL6e64\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV6GS6VL6e64&d=XETi2Bt%2BZpnTLEalwkJRlhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=c291d6c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V6GS6VL6e64</a>"},{"pid":"9cba9f0374e8d17b23933f8d46de757fc7555de5","tid":913610,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"